body.head: Doings of the County
Geddes News
body.p: Ed Dinsmore went ot Lake Andes Friday with Dr. Fyle. Prof. Murphy, of Platte, went to Aberdeen Monday to attend a meeting of county supertendents, called by teh state superintendents to discuss rural school problems.

Spring must be close at hand for the other day we saw Charley Hiett examining his fishing tackle and selecting the rods he expectes to use this season. A little early to do more than plan for fishing and yet the planning has its pleasures.
